e this pipeline was running. The verify stage completed after 1 retry but produced typecheck errors in the report, suggesting the retry may have passed without properly resolving the underlying TypeScript type mismatches in PagesPageConfig validation. | Failed at: ship | Suggestion: Add a `git fetch origin main` step before the ship stage's force-push to ensure the local ref is up-to-date with remote, and investigate whether the verify stage's retry logic is properly re-running type checks rather than passing cached results. | Flaw: ship — Git push rejected due to stale remote ref — no fetch/update before push | Stages: taskify:completed, plan:completed, build:completed, verify:completed, review:completed, review-fix:completed, ship:failed","createdAt":"2026-04-10T16:17:53.227Z","wordCount":963,"positions":[0,7,14,21,29,34,50,59,68,85,94,108,115,122,134,144,148,153,160,166,173,181,189,197,205,210,221,234,247,254,260,270,278,288,297,307,321,329,344,359,366,374,383,397,408,419,424,438,454,468,479,486,498,505,509,515,522,528,533,544,549,557,563,571,582,588,595,601,611,623,635,647,654,662,668,677,686,689,697,702,709,716,721,729,736,747,753,760,764,769,778,785,791,798,804,807,813,820,827,834,842,850,861,866,877,883,894,901,912,919,930,937,941,952,957]},"ep_stage_diary_001":{"taskId":"2306-260417-184459","episodeId":"ep_stage_diary_001","source":"stage_diary","content":"{\"stage\":\"review\",\"insights\":[{\"kind\":\"lesson\",\"text\":\"For external npm packages (like @kody-ade/engine), verification is done by inspecting the installed CLI binary in node_modules, not by modifying source.\",\"scope\":\"pipeline verification\"},{\"kind\":\"convention\",\"text\":\"Chore tasks (read-only verification) have no build step and no source changes; the implementation is just writing verify.md with PASS/FAIL.\",\"scope\":\"pipeline verification\"},{\"kind\":\"gotcha\",\"text\":\"The compose skip-logic is gated on decomposeState.mergeOutcome === \\\"merged\\\" at line ~18312 in the compiled CLI binary.\",\"scope\":\"@kody compose\"},{\"kind\":\"decision\",\"text\":\"Phase 2 Verify + Review always run after a skipped merge, so retrying compose after failure always resumes from the verify stage.\",\"scope\":\"@kody compose\"}]}","createdAt":"2026-04-17T19:16:19.206Z","wordCount":801,"positions":[2,10,19,32,39,48,59,68,72,82,88,93,97,106,122,130,145,155,159,169,174,183,190,200,210,218,227,244,251,264,271,277,284,289,294,313,316,322,331,334,341,354,372,377,385,392,400,405,413,421,430,447,454,463,474,482,487,496,505,520,539,551,557,570,579,583,593,602,607,619,626,637,644,652,661,668,675,679,687,695,702,705,714,722,728,736,743,760,767,776,785,790]},"ep_stage_diary_002":{"taskId":"2306-260417-184459","episodeId":"ep_stage_diary_002","source":"stage_diary","content":"{\"stage\":\"review-fix\",\"insights\":[{\"kind\":\"lesson\",\"text\":\"External npm packages can be verified by reading their installed CLI binaries in node_modules rather than modifying source code\",\"scope\":\"verification\"},{\"kind\":\"decision\",\"text\":\"Chore/verification tasks that don't modify source are classified as low-risk and don't require implementation beyond a verdict file\",\"scope\":\"task classification\"},{\"kind\":\"gotcha\",\"text\":\"pnpm's node_modules layout uses scoped paths like .pnpm/@kody-ade+engine@0.4.0_*/node_modules/@kody-ade/engine/ — glob patterns needed for path-agnostic lookup\",\"scope\":\"pnpm monorepo\"}]}","createdAt":"2026-04-17T19:17:57.070Z","wordCount":615,"positions":[2,10,17,23,36,43,52,59,68,72,88,100,114,124,128,140,145,153,160,165,175,182,189,197,214,221,232,239,245,258,269,275,282,293,307,311,320,326,334,349,358,366,373,381,386,405,412,421,428,435,440,448,455,460,467,473,479,485,490,494,509,514,523,528,532,542,547,556,567,572,581,590,598,603]}},"totalDocs":3}